    {
      "id": "detailed_1_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_1",
      "description": "This vehicle is in good, well-maintained condition and is ready for its next owner. Mechanically, it runs smoothly with a consistent service history, and the interior has been kept clean with only minor signs of use. While the exterior paint still holds a nice shine, there are a few small stone chips and light surface scratches consistent with regular driving. Overall, it\u2019s a dependable and attractive car that offers a great balance of reliability and value.",
